(43, 6, 30, 11, 13, 3, 3, 'What sign shewest thou then', 'Signs and Belief', 'This connection highlights the theme of signs as a means to inspire belief. In both passages, the request for a sign is central to the narrative, emphasizing the importance of divine confirmation in faith.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
